[
    {
        "source_sentence": "大般若波羅蜜多經卷第三百三",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541a25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三藏法師玄奘奉　詔譯",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541a27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "◎初分魔事品第四十之一",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541a28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，具壽善現白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541a29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛已讚說為證無上正等菩提，修行六種波羅蜜多，成熟有情、嚴淨佛國，諸善男子、善女人等所有功德。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541a29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b02_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "云何是善男子、善女人等，為證無上正等菩提修諸行時，留難魔事？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩樂說法要，辯不即生，當知是為菩薩魔事。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何故是菩薩摩訶薩樂說法要，辯不即生，是為魔事？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b07_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩修行般若波羅蜜多時，所修般若波羅蜜多難得圓滿，所修靜慮、精進、安忍、淨戒、布施波羅蜜多難得圓滿。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由此緣故，是菩薩摩訶薩樂說法要，辯不即生，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩樂修勝行，辯乃卒生，當知是為菩薩魔事。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何故是菩薩摩訶薩樂修勝行，辯乃卒生，是為魔事？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是菩薩摩訶薩修行布施波羅蜜多，修行淨戒、安忍、精進、靜慮、般若波羅蜜多，無巧便故，辯乃卒生。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "由此緣故，是菩薩摩訶薩樂修勝行，辯乃卒生，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b17_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b19_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "書寫般若波羅蜜多甚深經時頻申欠呿，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b19_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "書寫般若波羅蜜多甚深經時忽然戲笑，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "書寫般若波羅蜜多甚深經時互相輕蔑，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "書寫般若波羅蜜多甚深經時身心擾亂，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "書寫般若波羅蜜多甚深經時心生異解，文句倒錯，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "書寫般若波羅蜜多甚深經時欻有事起令不究竟，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541b29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "書寫般若波羅蜜多甚深經時忽作是念：『我於此經不得滋味，何用書寫？』",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "便棄捨去，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c05_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受持、讀誦、思惟、修習、說聽般若波羅蜜多甚深經時頻申欠呿，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受持、讀誦、思惟、修習、說聽般若波羅蜜多甚深經時忽然戲笑，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c11_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受持、讀誦、思惟、修習、說聽般若波羅蜜多甚深經時互相輕蔑，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c14_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受持、讀誦、思惟、修習、說聽般若波羅蜜多甚深經時身心擾亂，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c17_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受持、讀誦、思惟、修習、說聽般若波羅蜜多甚深經時心生異解，文句倒錯，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c17_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受持、讀誦、思惟、修習、說聽般若波羅蜜多甚深經時欻有事起令不究竟，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "受持、讀誦、思惟、修習、說聽般若波羅蜜多甚深經時，忽作是念：『我於此經不得滋味，何用勤苦？』",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c23_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "便棄捨去，當知是為菩薩魔事。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c25_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，具壽善現白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何因緣故，是善男子、善女人等，於此深經不得滋味，便棄捨去？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c29_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人等，於過去世未久修行般若、靜慮、精進、安忍、淨戒、布施波羅蜜多，是故於此甚深般若波羅蜜多不得滋味，便棄捨去。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0541c29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人等，聞說如是甚深般若波羅蜜多，便作是念：『我等於此不得受記，何用聽為？』",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心不清淨，便從座起棄捨而去，當知是為菩薩魔事。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，具壽善現白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何因緣故，於此般若波羅蜜多甚深經中，不授彼記而令捨去？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a10_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩未入正性離生，不應授彼大菩提記。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人等，聞說如是甚深般若波羅蜜多，便作是念：『此中不說我等名字，何用聽為？』",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心不清淨，便從座起棄捨而去，當知是為菩薩魔事。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，具壽善現白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何因緣故，於此般若波羅蜜多甚深經中，不記說彼菩薩名字？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "菩薩未受大菩提記，法爾不應記說名字。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a18_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若善男子、善女人等，聞說般若波羅蜜多甚深經時，生如是念：『此中不說我等生處城邑聚落，何用聽為？』",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "心不清淨，便從座起棄捨而去，當知是為菩薩魔事。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a22_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，具壽善現白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何因緣故，於此般若波羅蜜多甚深經中，不記說彼菩薩生處城邑聚落？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a24_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若未記彼菩薩名字，不應說其生處差別。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a28_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩，聞說般若波羅蜜多，心不清淨而捨去者，隨彼所起不清淨心，厭捨此經舉步多少，便減爾所劫數功德，獲爾所劫障菩提罪，受彼罪已更爾所時，發勤精進求趣無上正等菩提方可復本。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542a28_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是故菩薩若欲速證無上菩提，不應厭捨甚深般若波羅蜜多。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "住菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等，棄捨般若波羅蜜多甚深經典，求學餘經，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b06_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b08_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人等，棄捨一切智智根本甚深般若波羅蜜多，而攀枝葉諸餘經典，終不能得大菩提故。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，具壽善現白佛言：「世尊！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b12_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何等餘經猶如枝葉，不能引發一切智智？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b12_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若說二乘相應之法，謂四念住、四正斷、四神足、五根、五力、七等覺支、八聖道支及空、無相、無願解脫門等所有諸經，若善男子、善女人等於中修學，得預流果、得一來果、得不還果、得阿羅漢果、得獨覺菩提，不得無上正等菩提，是名餘經猶如枝葉，不能引發一切智智。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "甚深般若波羅蜜多定能引發一切智智，有大勢力猶如樹根。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人等，棄捨般若波羅蜜多甚深經典求學餘經，定不能得一切智智。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b21_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b22_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b23_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是般若波羅蜜多甚深經典，出生一切菩薩摩訶薩世間、出世間功德法故。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b23_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若菩薩摩訶薩修學般若波羅蜜多，則為修學一切世間、出世間法。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b27_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如餓狗捨其主食，返從僕使而求覓之，於當來世有菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等，棄捨一切佛法根本甚深般若波羅蜜多，求學二乘相應經典亦復如是，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542b27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有人欲求香象，得此象已捨而求跡。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c03_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何？",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人有智不？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現答言：「是人無智。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c05_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於當來世有菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等，棄捨一切佛法根本甚深般若波羅蜜多，求學二乘相應經典亦復如是，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有人欲見大海，既至海岸返觀牛跡，作是念言：『大海中水淺深多少豈及此耶？』",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c09_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何？",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人有智不？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現答言：「是人無智。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c12_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於當來世有菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等，棄捨一切佛法根本甚深般若波羅蜜多，求學二乘相應經典亦復如是，當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c12_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c16_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如有工匠或彼弟子，欲造大殿如天帝釋殊勝殿量，見彼殿已而返揆摸日月宮殿。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是工匠或彼弟子，能造大殿量如帝釋殊勝殿不？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c18_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現答言：「不也！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c19_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c20_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何？",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c20_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人有智不？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c20_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現答言：「是人無智，是愚癡類。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c20_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於當來世有菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等，欲求無上正等菩提，棄捨如是甚深般若波羅蜜多，求學二乘相應經典亦復如是。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c24_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人等，能得無上佛菩提不？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c25_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現答言「不也！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c26_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c26_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人等是黠慧不？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c26_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現答言：「是愚癡類。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c28_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c28_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是為菩薩魔事。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0542c28_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0543a01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如人求見轉輪聖王，見已不識捨至餘處，見凡小王取其形相，作如是念：『轉輪聖王形相威德與此何異？』",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0543a01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於汝意云何？",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0543a03_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人有智不？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0543a03_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現答言：「是人無智。」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0543a04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛言：「善現！",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0543a04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於當來世有菩薩乘諸善男子、善女人等，欲求無上正等菩提，棄捨如是甚深般若波羅蜜多，求學二乘相應經典亦復如是。",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0543a04_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0543a07_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是善男子、善女人等，為能證得大菩提不？」",
        "from": "T06n0220_303:0543a08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善現答言：「不也！",
